        <div class="favourite">
            <i id="wishlist-icon" class="far fa-star"></i><p>Wishlist</p>
        </div>

        <p class="description">The Sony Alpha 9 II is a high-performance full-frame mirrorless camera designed for professional photographers and advanced enthusiasts. It features a 24.2-megapixel sensor and a powerful BIONZ X processor, delivering fast and accurate autofocus, as well as exceptional image quality. The camera offers continuous shooting speeds of up to 20 frames per second with no blackout, allowing you to capture fast-moving subjects with precision. Its advanced autofocus system includes 693 phase-detection points for precise tracking and focus.
